body:
Perma ban for being toxic is the stupidest shit I&#039;ve ever heard. People are toxic in general. How can you sit there and say &quot;I only want nice people to play my game, even though they have spent a lot of their hard earned money for further enjoyment&quot;

I admit.. sometimes I get excessive with language and the way that I speak to people on this game... but to permanently ban my account so easily... I mean look... if you&#039;re going to perma ban someone... at least ban them for a month first... or 3 months... or even 6 months. I understand, lots of people share the perspective that someone who talks shit should be gone permanently... but you might as well be saying that anyone that talks shit should be dead. You think people gave a damn about someone talking shit back in the medieval ages? We are at war in league. Some of us have had hard lives and use video games as an outlet instead of raging in real life. Some of us get raged at in life growing up and use video games as an escape from this and can find themselves raging in game. Not everyone gets to grow up in nice setting with a good family or people around that respect them.

On my account I had every single champion... so many skins... full tab of rune pages... history... and now it&#039;s just gone with no chance of return? How can that be fair? I was unaware, at the time, that you get perma ban directly after 14 day chat restriction... If I had known.. I most definitely wouldn&#039;t have said anything at all. I&#039;ve been chat restricted a lot over the years because I&#039;m an angry mother fucker... I thought it was something like that... but no... BAM perma ban first game back after 14 day suspension LOL. GGNORE league
